&lt;p&gt;Two calls to readPassword() ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13880319" author="tripod" created="Thu, 23 Jan 2014 20:26:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;rcp&lt;/tt&gt; currently needs the credentials passed in the URL, which is not secure. but it should fall back to the credentials stored in the &lt;tt&gt;~/.vault/auth.xml&lt;/tt&gt;. but also prompt for 2 passwords is probably feasible.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
